\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/06\/05\/allah-turns-heart-how-wills\/","url_meta":{"origin":32218,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Hearts: O Allah, keep my heart steadfast upon Islam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 5, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would often say, \u201cO Turner of the hearts, keep my heart firm upon Your religion!\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2140 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u064a\u064f\u0643\u0652\u062b\u0650\u0631\u064f \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u064a\u064e\u0642\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15287,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/22\/eat-walking-drink-standing\/","url_meta":{"origin":32218,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Manners: Concession to eat walking, drink standing","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 22, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: In the lifetime of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, we would eat while walking and drink while standing. Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1880 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0642\u064e\u